data.description: Three bedroom home on a large corner lot offers a charming country feel while still being close to modern conveniences. This is a fixer-upper! Roll up your sleeves and put in some work here. Perfect opportunity for rehabbers and investors. Spacious eat-in kitchen with vaulted ceilings, skylights, ceiling fan, and separate entrance. Carpeted living room off the front entrance area. Spacious main bedroom. Front porch, shade trees, and detached 2 car garage. Come add your finishing touch! Award winning Crystal Lake schools!
